  readyLine="Your Agent Voice Architecture Guide is ready."
  downloadHeading="Download your guide"
  downloadHref="/downloads/Agent-Voice-Architecture-Guide-v1.0.pdf"
>
  <Fragment slot="download-description">
    <p>The Agent Voice Architecture Guide covers voice design principles, extraction vs. sovereignty language, voice specification templates, quality checks, and refusal voice patterns.</p>
    <p>Start with Part 2: the extraction vs. sovereignty language table. It will change how you hear your agents.</p>
