  <Fragment slot="next-steps">
    <a href="/products/agent-voice-architecture-guide" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Run the voice audit</h3>
      <p>Use the 12-point Pre-Deployment Voice Audit in Part 4 on your existing agents. It takes 15 minutes.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Open the guide page &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/trust-architecture-blueprint" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Go deeper</h3>
